entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: Borvo tricked you into breaking into his own vault to test the security, but you acquired the droid part, and there seems to be no hard feelings from Borvo.
entries.journal_entry_description: Borvo has offered you the computer part you want, at no charge. This seems like a trick.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Borvo gave you the location of his vault. You should head there and see if you can break in.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: There are 8 security codes to override before you can open the vault in the back.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: You've done it! Congratulations. Now all you have to do is make it to the vault and get your precious part.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Make your way to the back of the vault and get the droid AI.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Make your way back to Borvo and let him know you got your AI from his vault.
